{"content": "I need to multiply 882 \u00d7 842 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 882\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 8\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 648 + 72 + 2 = 722\u2081\u2080\n- 842\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 648 + 36 + 2 = 686\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 722 \u00d7 686 = 495,292\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 495292 \u00f7 9 = 55032 r 4\n- 55032 \u00f7 9 = 6114 r 6\n- 6114 \u00f7 9 = 679 r 3\n- 679 \u00f7 9 = 75 r 4\n- 75 \u00f7 9 = 8 r 3\n- 8 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 8\n\nReading from bottom to top: **834364\u2089**\n\n834364", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 344}